WEBVTT

01:31.050 --> 01:34.979
[Dream of Golden Years]

01:35.920 --> 01:39.479
[2006]

02:02.960 --> 02:04.350
Ms. Tian, please go back.

02:04.350 --> 02:05.070
Haven't I made it

02:05.070 --> 02:06.200
very clear to you?

02:06.310 --> 02:07.090
Go back. Just go back.

02:07.090 --> 02:08.630
My uncle can marry into your family.

02:08.630 --> 02:09.710
You won't lose anything,

02:09.710 --> 02:10.190
right?

02:10.520 --> 02:11.560
Your uncle...

02:11.560 --> 02:12.400
Let me tell you,

02:12.400 --> 02:13.490
he's a drunkard.

02:13.520 --> 02:14.430
He beat his wife, too.

02:14.430 --> 02:15.260
With conditions like that,

02:15.260 --> 02:16.300
how could he possibly come to our house

02:16.300 --> 02:17.050
to propose?

02:17.079 --> 02:17.560
Right?

02:18.840 --> 02:19.520
Fen.

02:19.750 --> 02:20.180
Look.

02:20.430 --> 02:22.079
Xiaolan will get married sooner or later,

02:22.079 --> 02:22.560
right?

02:22.750 --> 02:23.960
Whether Xiaolan gets married or not,

02:23.960 --> 02:24.710
what does it have to do with your family?

02:24.710 --> 02:25.910
How is it not related?

02:25.960 --> 02:27.240
My uncle is quite nice.

02:27.240 --> 02:29.120
He and Fen are a good match.

02:29.120 --> 02:31.120
I tell you, don't make random matches.

02:31.120 --> 02:32.310
As I told you, they're not suitable.

02:32.310 --> 02:33.570
I'm not making random—

02:33.980 --> 02:35.079
Why are there so many people?

02:35.079 --> 02:35.800
It's quite lively.

02:35.800 --> 02:37.680
What are you doing? You damn old woman!

02:37.680 --> 02:38.400
Sorry.

02:38.890 --> 02:39.930
Alright, go back.

02:39.960 --> 02:41.610
I've made it very clear to you.

02:41.610 --> 02:42.810
Go back. Just go back.

02:43.030 --> 02:45.030
As I told you, they're not suitable.

02:45.150 --> 02:45.680
Right?

02:45.840 --> 02:47.280
You look down on my uncle?

02:47.840 --> 02:48.960
I'd like to see what kind of family

02:48.960 --> 02:50.220
Liu Fen can marry into.

02:50.750 --> 02:52.120
What the hell?

02:52.310 --> 02:53.590
She splashed water all over me!

02:53.590 --> 02:54.960
You are afraid of offending

02:54.960 --> 02:56.430
these neighbors.

02:57.000 --> 02:58.430
I'm all alone.

02:59.190 --> 03:00.050
I'm not afraid.

03:00.620 --> 03:01.820
Granny Yu, well done.

03:03.560 --> 03:04.280
Well,

03:04.450 --> 03:05.870
thank you, Uncles and Aunties,

03:05.870 --> 03:07.750
for worrying about my mom's remarriage.

03:07.750 --> 03:08.630
But now, we

03:08.630 --> 03:10.190
have settled in Shengcheng.

03:10.190 --> 03:11.630
So we won't trouble you anymore.

03:11.630 --> 03:12.280
It's the New Year.

03:12.280 --> 03:13.630
Everyone, please go back.

03:13.630 --> 03:14.550
Happy New Year.

03:15.000 --> 03:16.190
Go prepare your New Year's goods.

03:16.190 --> 03:16.630
Yes, yes.

03:16.630 --> 03:17.490
Happy New Year.

03:18.079 --> 03:18.480
Hurry.

03:19.190 --> 03:20.150
Go back quickly.

03:21.030 --> 03:21.960
Come on, come on.

03:23.120 --> 03:23.870
Xiaolan.

03:24.280 --> 03:25.120
Let me tell you,

03:25.120 --> 03:26.960
you should hurry up

03:26.960 --> 03:28.120
with the recruitment.

03:28.120 --> 03:30.240
Go back to Shengcheng
right after the New Year.

03:30.240 --> 03:30.710
You see,

03:31.079 --> 03:33.120
you and your mother are living so well.

03:33.120 --> 03:34.800
Those people are jealous.

03:35.079 --> 03:36.720
They won't give up easily.

03:36.910 --> 03:37.590
I'm back.

03:38.190 --> 03:39.920
Someone came to propose again?

03:42.400 --> 03:42.930
Xiaolan,

03:43.310 --> 03:44.430
which family is it? Tell me.

03:44.430 --> 03:45.750
I'll go have a chat with them.

03:45.750 --> 03:46.750
Forget it, Uncle.

03:46.960 --> 03:48.120
We don't come back often.

03:48.120 --> 03:49.750
There's no need to argue with them.

03:49.750 --> 03:50.840
We really should

03:50.840 --> 03:52.180
get the recruiting done first.

03:52.180 --> 03:53.750
When we bring benefits to the village,

03:53.750 --> 03:55.030
people will naturally speak up for us.

03:55.030 --> 03:55.590
Exactly.

03:55.750 --> 03:57.030
Once our family makes money

03:57.030 --> 03:57.800
and thinks of everyone,

03:57.800 --> 03:59.240
helping them live a better life,

03:59.240 --> 03:59.800
they'll naturally stand

03:59.800 --> 04:00.840
on our side.

04:01.520 --> 04:02.410
True.

04:02.890 --> 04:03.240
Let's go.

04:03.240 --> 04:04.590
Let's go talk to the Chief.

04:04.590 --> 04:05.430
Unload the stuff then.

04:05.430 --> 04:06.090
Okay, okay.

04:08.560 --> 04:09.030
Look.

04:09.120 --> 04:10.840
Guangdong sausage.

04:11.470 --> 04:12.000
Nice.

04:12.960 --> 04:13.820
Yong.

04:14.000 --> 04:15.600
Thinking of the villagers

04:15.630 --> 04:16.589
shows your kindness.

04:16.589 --> 04:17.360
Don't worry.

04:17.560 --> 04:21.160
[Qijing Village Villagers Committee]

04:17.870 --> 04:18.920
As for the recruitment,

04:18.920 --> 04:20.560
I'll definitely handle it for you.

04:20.560 --> 04:21.120
Great.

04:21.510 --> 04:21.920
Later,

04:21.920 --> 04:22.830
have them come to my house tomorrow

04:22.830 --> 04:23.390
for a meal.

04:23.390 --> 04:24.870
We'll discuss it properly.

04:24.870 --> 04:25.270
Sure.

04:25.730 --> 04:27.160
Once the people are picked,

04:27.160 --> 04:27.800
I'll have them

04:27.800 --> 04:28.830
come to your house.

04:28.830 --> 04:29.160
Good.

04:30.160 --> 04:30.830
Xiaolan.

04:31.240 --> 04:31.970
Don't worry.

04:32.190 --> 04:33.190
I told them all

04:33.480 --> 04:34.340
not to meddle in

04:34.390 --> 04:35.590
your mom's business.

04:35.720 --> 04:36.560
You two just

04:36.870 --> 04:38.360
have a peaceful New Year.

04:38.630 --> 04:39.630
Thank you, Chief.

04:39.900 --> 04:40.950
By the way, Yong.

04:41.430 --> 04:42.800
Isn't Tao's cousin

04:42.800 --> 04:44.260
coming back for the New Year?

04:44.260 --> 04:45.230
Tao's cousin?

04:46.270 --> 04:48.130
Since when does Tao have a cousin?

04:49.560 --> 04:50.220
Zhou Cheng?

04:52.020 --> 04:52.750
Chief.

04:53.159 --> 04:54.600
Tao doesn't have a cousin.

04:54.600 --> 04:56.400
That Zhou Cheng, actually he...

04:58.159 --> 04:59.510
I knew it long ago.

05:00.160 --> 05:02.300
That kid seems nice.

05:02.560 --> 05:04.220
He's a good match for Xiaolan.

05:05.220 --> 05:05.870
Xiaolan,

05:06.310 --> 05:07.190
next time he comes,

05:07.190 --> 05:08.070
introduce him

05:08.160 --> 05:09.870
to the villagers properly.

05:11.270 --> 05:12.070
Sure.

05:12.310 --> 05:12.720
Okay.

05:13.190 --> 05:14.270
Come over in the next couple of days

05:14.270 --> 05:15.160
for a meal,

05:15.630 --> 05:16.680
so you can try

05:16.680 --> 05:17.940
the Shengcheng cuisine.

05:17.940 --> 05:18.740
That's great.

05:19.120 --> 05:20.680
I'll try the Shengcheng cuisine.

05:20.680 --> 05:21.210
Alright.

05:21.270 --> 05:22.090
-Bye.
-Okay.

05:22.190 --> 05:22.520
Okay.

05:22.560 --> 05:22.890
Okay.

05:22.950 --> 05:23.720
Take care.

05:25.160 --> 05:25.830
Granny Yu.

05:26.240 --> 05:26.970
You're back.

05:28.310 --> 05:29.070
When you weren't here,

05:29.070 --> 05:30.720
Zhou Cheng called to say

05:31.560 --> 05:33.920
he's coming for a New Year visit
on the second day.

05:33.920 --> 05:34.480
Really?

05:34.750 --> 05:35.880
What else did he say?

05:37.560 --> 05:38.950
To an old woman like me,

05:39.240 --> 05:40.370
what is there to say?

05:41.040 --> 05:42.830
If there's something
you want to hear from him,

05:42.830 --> 05:44.360
just call him back.

05:54.680 --> 05:56.409
Is the phone burning your hand?

06:01.890 --> 06:02.970
Okay, let's go.

06:03.680 --> 06:05.480
Be careful. Slow down. Slow down.

06:05.480 --> 06:06.800
Watch out for your feet.

06:06.800 --> 06:07.850
Careful. Careful.

06:07.850 --> 06:08.680
Careful. Good.

06:08.680 --> 06:09.480
Yong!

06:11.000 --> 06:12.260
Wait a moment. Come on.

06:12.730 --> 06:13.160
-Come on!
-Come on!

06:13.160 --> 06:14.950
-Give us a hand, everyone!
-Give us a hand!

06:14.950 --> 06:15.800
-Come on, come on.
-Come on, come on.

06:15.800 --> 06:16.510
Okay, okay.

06:17.000 --> 06:17.680
Yong.

06:18.040 --> 06:19.270
Uncle Da said
if we went to the city with you,

06:19.270 --> 06:20.280
we could make money,

06:20.280 --> 06:21.200
so we came.

06:21.750 --> 06:23.360
You can definitely make money,

06:23.360 --> 06:25.390
but it will be hard work.

06:25.750 --> 06:27.350
Can you handle the hardship?

06:27.390 --> 06:28.050
-Yes.
-Yes.

06:28.480 --> 06:29.810
-We can.
-We surely can.

06:30.330 --> 06:31.790
Then move the chairs over.

06:31.800 --> 06:32.560
Sit down, and we'll talk!

06:32.560 --> 06:33.480
-Come on, come on!
-Come on, come on!

06:33.480 --> 06:34.950
The legs of lamb are here.

06:34.950 --> 06:36.950
Look at these great legs of lamb.

06:37.480 --> 06:37.950
Look.

06:38.000 --> 06:38.800
Really good.

06:39.040 --> 06:41.070
Granny Yu,
how should we cook these legs of lamb?

06:41.070 --> 06:42.040
Braise one,

06:42.270 --> 06:43.870
and make soup with the other.

06:44.310 --> 06:45.370
You're a good cook.

06:45.510 --> 06:46.440
You make the soup.

06:46.440 --> 06:48.159
Didn't we say we'd braise them yesterday?

06:48.159 --> 06:49.480
Why are we making soup today?

06:49.480 --> 06:51.600
If Granny Yu says we should make soup,
we'll do it.

06:51.600 --> 06:52.360
But I won't put

06:52.360 --> 06:53.360
potatoes in.

06:53.560 --> 06:55.560
Eating potatoes raises blood sugar.

06:55.560 --> 06:57.090
You should be more careful.

06:58.030 --> 06:59.750
She nags more than a doctor.

07:00.240 --> 07:00.840
Granny Yu.

07:01.560 --> 07:02.560
Today, you are

07:02.560 --> 07:04.000
acting a bit differently than usual.

07:04.000 --> 07:05.060
It's a bit strange.

07:06.190 --> 07:06.920
Really?

07:08.920 --> 07:09.660
Yong.

07:10.190 --> 07:12.190
I found these people strictly following

07:12.190 --> 07:13.320
your requirements.

07:14.270 --> 07:15.530
We all know each other.

07:15.640 --> 07:17.100
Happy New Year, everyone.

07:19.800 --> 07:20.410
Have a taste.

07:20.410 --> 07:21.470
Let's eat and talk.

07:21.480 --> 07:22.210
Listen to me.

07:23.000 --> 07:24.390
These past few years,

07:24.390 --> 07:25.630
I've been in Shengcheng,

07:25.630 --> 07:27.360
renovating houses for people.

07:27.750 --> 07:29.510
Business is getting better and better.

07:29.510 --> 07:31.160
Now I'm short of hands.

07:31.750 --> 07:33.270
I need people I know well

07:33.270 --> 07:34.270
who can do the job.

07:34.890 --> 07:35.530
Naturally,

07:35.530 --> 07:37.120
I prefer folks from our village,

07:37.120 --> 07:37.520
right?

07:37.560 --> 07:39.830
-Right, right.
-Right, right.

07:39.920 --> 07:40.800
Let me tell you.

07:40.830 --> 07:42.240
Even if you have bricklaying skills,

07:42.240 --> 07:44.370
you have to start from scratch with me.

07:45.070 --> 07:46.670
When you first start with me,

07:46.700 --> 07:48.770
I can pay you 10 yuan a day.

07:48.800 --> 07:49.480
Ten yuan.

07:49.720 --> 07:51.520
When you become a junior worker,

07:51.920 --> 07:52.750
it's 13 a day.

07:53.810 --> 07:54.920
-Thirteen yuan!
-Thirteen!

07:54.920 --> 07:56.480
When you become a senior worker,

07:56.480 --> 07:59.070
I'll pay you 18 yuan a day!

08:00.600 --> 08:01.950
I want to be a senior worker!

08:01.950 --> 08:03.120
I want to be a senior worker too!

08:03.120 --> 08:05.160
Although we've never been to Shengcheng,

08:05.160 --> 08:07.040
we've all done unskilled labor in Shangdu.

08:07.040 --> 08:08.380
The wage Yong offers

08:08.480 --> 08:09.270
is really fair,

08:09.270 --> 08:09.680
right?

08:09.700 --> 08:10.900
-Totally!
-Totally!

08:11.270 --> 08:11.870
Last year,

08:11.870 --> 08:12.920
I worked in the county town

08:12.920 --> 08:14.320
and only made 8 yuan a day.

08:15.510 --> 08:17.120
Everyone understands the money situation,

08:17.120 --> 08:17.520
right?

08:18.070 --> 08:19.720
Let me tell you something else.

08:19.720 --> 08:20.750
The train tickets

08:21.040 --> 08:21.570
are on me!

08:24.680 --> 08:26.630
Everyone has

08:26.630 --> 08:27.480
ID cards now, right?

08:27.480 --> 08:28.190
You all got them, right?

08:28.190 --> 08:29.630
-We got them.
-We got them.

08:29.630 --> 08:30.830
So for the tickets,

08:30.960 --> 08:32.510
we don't need letters of introduction
anymore.

08:32.510 --> 08:33.770
It's more convenient.

08:33.840 --> 08:35.080
That is so convenient.

08:35.080 --> 08:35.880
That's great.

08:36.630 --> 08:37.159
Fengmei.

08:37.490 --> 08:38.549
What are you cooking?

08:38.549 --> 08:39.610
It smells so great!

08:40.130 --> 08:41.330
You'll find out soon.

08:41.360 --> 08:43.250
I promise you'll eat and drink your fill.

08:43.250 --> 08:44.840
-Great!
-Great!

08:44.870 --> 08:46.200
Today, right here,

08:46.630 --> 08:48.030
enjoy the food and drink.

08:48.120 --> 08:48.840
Then,

08:49.030 --> 08:50.030
go home and explain everything

08:50.030 --> 08:51.550
clearly to your wives and children.

08:51.550 --> 08:52.670
Then we'll head out!

08:52.670 --> 08:54.320
-Okay!
-Okay!

08:54.390 --> 08:56.530
-Thanks, Yong!
-Thanks, Yong!

09:00.080 --> 09:01.440
Is the meat ready?

09:01.720 --> 09:02.550
It smells so good.

09:02.550 --> 09:03.350
Wait a moment.

09:03.670 --> 09:05.130
Let the sauce reduce a bit.

09:05.320 --> 09:06.670
The food is almost ready, right?

09:06.670 --> 09:07.600
I think it's time

09:07.600 --> 09:08.320
to start the feast.

09:08.320 --> 09:09.240
It's time to eat.

09:09.240 --> 09:10.240
What's the rush?

09:11.030 --> 09:13.430
Wait for your uncle
to settle the business.

09:13.440 --> 09:14.240
Otherwise, in a bit,

09:14.240 --> 09:15.410
they'll be drunk,

09:15.440 --> 09:17.240
leaving the business unsettled

09:17.320 --> 09:18.790
and bickering over nothing.

09:18.790 --> 09:19.390
True.

09:19.600 --> 09:20.270
These men

09:20.270 --> 09:21.960
drink endlessly during the New Year.

09:21.960 --> 09:22.670
Exactly.

09:26.440 --> 09:27.440
Granny Yu,

09:27.840 --> 09:28.840
why does it look like

09:28.840 --> 09:30.440
you are waiting for someone?

09:34.600 --> 09:36.200
Yong, your relative is here!

09:37.790 --> 09:39.520
-Who else is coming?
-Who is it?

09:39.550 --> 09:40.320
Let's go see.

09:41.630 --> 09:42.960
Thank you for your help.

09:43.200 --> 09:43.730
Who is it?

09:44.550 --> 09:45.030
Mr. Liu.

09:47.200 --> 09:47.730
Xiaolan.

09:49.290 --> 09:49.910
Mr. Tang.

09:49.910 --> 09:50.270
Well.

09:50.600 --> 09:52.150
W-What brings you here?

09:52.840 --> 09:54.880
I'm visiting unannounced.

09:54.910 --> 09:56.240
I really apologize.

09:58.200 --> 09:58.960
Who is it?

10:07.320 --> 10:07.910
Who is it?

10:08.790 --> 10:09.480
The Mayor.

10:09.480 --> 10:10.840
I haven't been to Yunan

10:10.840 --> 10:11.720
for a long time.

10:11.750 --> 10:12.240
This place

10:12.240 --> 10:13.440
is indeed quite cold.

10:13.550 --> 10:13.910
Yes.

10:13.930 --> 10:15.220
Well, give them to me.

10:15.720 --> 10:16.510
Inside. This way.

10:16.510 --> 10:16.960
Welcome.

10:16.960 --> 10:17.790
All right, all right.

10:17.790 --> 10:18.390
Thank you.

10:18.960 --> 10:20.390
Go get a bowl of mutton soup

10:20.390 --> 10:21.270
for him.

10:21.910 --> 10:22.270
Okay.

10:22.480 --> 10:23.340
Please come in.

10:23.450 --> 10:24.390
Inside, please.

10:24.390 --> 10:25.270
Hello, folks.

10:25.270 --> 10:26.740
Why is the Mayor visiting our home?

10:26.740 --> 10:27.860
How should I know?

10:28.440 --> 10:28.960
Let's go.

10:28.960 --> 10:30.080
Let's go inside.

10:30.600 --> 10:31.240
Granny Yu.

10:31.840 --> 10:32.470
Nice to meet you.

10:32.470 --> 10:33.670
Welcome, welcome.

10:34.670 --> 10:35.750
Here, Mayor Tang.

10:36.400 --> 10:37.670
Have some tea to warm up.

10:37.670 --> 10:38.200
Let me get it. Let me.

10:38.200 --> 10:38.630
I can manage.

10:38.630 --> 10:39.570
Let me get it. Let me.

10:39.570 --> 10:40.030
No need to be polite.

10:40.030 --> 10:41.240
Alright, thank you.

10:41.550 --> 10:42.750
It's cold. Have some soup.

10:42.750 --> 10:43.480
Mutton soup.

10:45.970 --> 10:47.270
Did you make this soup?

10:51.480 --> 10:52.030
It's hot.

10:55.240 --> 10:55.880
This soup

10:55.910 --> 10:57.110
is really authentic.

10:57.960 --> 10:58.510
One sip,

10:58.790 --> 10:59.990
and I'm warm all over.

11:01.040 --> 11:02.370
Alright, you guys chat.

11:04.760 --> 11:05.550
During the New Year,

11:05.550 --> 11:07.010
you have to come back home.

11:07.210 --> 11:08.480
Being with fellow villagers

11:08.480 --> 11:09.390
and friends,

11:09.480 --> 11:10.200
cracking sunflower seeds

11:10.200 --> 11:11.000
and chatting,

11:11.030 --> 11:11.790
is such a joy.

11:11.870 --> 11:13.790
-Yes, indeed.
-Yeah.

11:14.120 --> 11:16.120
I'd like to give you an update.

11:16.390 --> 11:17.240
After the New Year,

11:17.240 --> 11:17.790
I plan

11:17.790 --> 11:18.750
to take these folks

11:18.750 --> 11:20.020
to work in Shengcheng.

11:21.200 --> 11:22.800
Going to Shengcheng is good.

11:22.870 --> 11:23.790
Shengcheng

11:23.790 --> 11:25.120
is developing fast now,

11:25.240 --> 11:26.670
with so many job opportunities.

11:26.670 --> 11:27.870
As long as you go there

11:27.960 --> 11:29.440
and are willing to work hard,

11:29.440 --> 11:30.600
you will definitely make money.

11:30.600 --> 11:31.000
Right.

11:31.120 --> 11:33.320
-Yes.
-Yes, as long as we can make money.

11:33.320 --> 11:35.080
You look familiar.

11:35.390 --> 11:36.790
-You are County—
-Chief.

11:37.240 --> 11:37.690
You can just

11:37.690 --> 11:39.240
call me Comrade Tang.

11:39.870 --> 11:41.440
Anything else feels distant.

11:41.440 --> 11:41.790
Okay.

11:41.950 --> 11:42.510
Comrade it is.

11:42.510 --> 11:43.790
Hello, Comrade Tang.

11:44.250 --> 11:44.910
Sit down, Chief.

11:44.910 --> 11:45.200
Please, sit.

11:45.200 --> 11:46.440
Have some sunflower seeds, please.

11:46.440 --> 11:47.100
Okay, okay.

11:47.480 --> 11:48.410
No formalities.

11:48.550 --> 11:49.510
We're all friends here.

11:49.510 --> 11:49.930
Okay, okay.

11:49.930 --> 11:50.720
Thank you. Thank you.

11:50.720 --> 11:51.180
Thanks.

11:51.320 --> 11:51.910
Come on.

11:53.750 --> 11:54.240
Chief,

11:54.550 --> 11:55.480
what's wrong?

11:56.320 --> 11:57.520
What's wrong with me?

11:57.910 --> 11:59.080
I'm just happy.

11:59.510 --> 12:00.720
A distinguished guest
has come to our village.

12:00.720 --> 12:01.910
Can't I be happy?

12:03.200 --> 12:03.720
Happy.

12:03.770 --> 12:04.320
Right?

12:04.320 --> 12:04.720
Happy.

12:06.150 --> 12:06.550
Delighted.

12:06.550 --> 12:07.630
Hey, Yong.

12:08.080 --> 12:09.680
Your business in Shengcheng

12:09.870 --> 12:11.180
has really grown.

12:11.210 --> 12:11.720
No, no.

12:11.750 --> 12:12.630
It's alright.

12:13.080 --> 12:13.510
Here.

12:19.440 --> 12:20.670
He drank it all.

12:21.840 --> 12:22.200
Here.

12:22.830 --> 12:24.360
Another bowl for the Mayor.

12:24.420 --> 12:25.440
Another bowl?

12:33.320 --> 12:34.670
So Granny Yu's soup

12:34.670 --> 12:36.330
was ordered for someone else.

12:43.600 --> 12:44.000
Hello?

12:44.910 --> 12:45.600
Zhou Cheng.

12:47.480 --> 12:48.610
Xiaolan isn't here.

12:49.160 --> 12:50.960
She's gone to the Chief's house.

12:51.750 --> 12:52.200
Okay.

12:52.910 --> 12:53.790
I'll tell her.

12:55.000 --> 12:56.930
Everything's fine in the village.

12:58.150 --> 13:00.610
Some people just play matchmakers blindly.

13:01.360 --> 13:04.000
For your future mother-in-law.

13:07.030 --> 13:07.440
Okay.

13:08.100 --> 13:09.160
I'm hanging up now.

13:17.120 --> 13:18.320
Don't they want to see

13:18.600 --> 13:19.840
what kind of person

13:19.840 --> 13:20.900
your mom will find?

13:21.430 --> 13:22.670
Let's show them.

13:23.200 --> 13:24.270
My mom and Mr. Tang?

13:26.000 --> 13:27.340
Your mom can't tell,

13:27.480 --> 13:29.120
but can't you tell?

13:29.550 --> 13:31.410
Think about it, it's the New Year.

13:31.440 --> 13:32.840
How could Tang stay alone

13:32.840 --> 13:34.080
in Shengcheng?

13:34.440 --> 13:35.970
Even if I hadn't called him,

13:36.120 --> 13:37.580
he would have come anyway.

13:37.720 --> 13:38.720
Do you believe me?

13:39.550 --> 13:40.950
I believe you. Of course.

13:40.970 --> 13:41.600
Granny Yu,

13:42.200 --> 13:43.130
you're amazing.

13:43.610 --> 13:44.840
Come, try this.

13:45.200 --> 13:45.810
Abalone.

13:45.840 --> 13:46.440
Mr. Tang.

13:46.720 --> 13:47.250
Seafood.

13:47.360 --> 13:48.000
Mr. Tang.

13:48.030 --> 13:48.480
Okay.

13:48.670 --> 13:49.440
Mr. Tang.

13:50.010 --> 13:51.550
I don't have very nice clothes here,

13:51.550 --> 13:52.480
but this is warm.

13:52.540 --> 13:53.670
That's great, Yong.

13:53.670 --> 13:54.840
You've solved a big problem for me.

13:54.840 --> 13:56.480
Alright, as long as it's warm,

13:56.480 --> 13:57.000
Mr. Tang.

13:57.000 --> 13:57.960
Thank you. Thank you.

13:57.960 --> 13:58.560
Sit, Yong.

13:58.960 --> 14:00.360
Don't call me Mr. Tang.

14:01.080 --> 14:02.240
We're about the same age,

14:02.240 --> 14:03.510
and we've known each other for so long.

14:03.510 --> 14:04.360
Just call me Tang.

14:04.360 --> 14:05.290
I wouldn't dare.

14:05.320 --> 14:06.000
Why wouldn't you?

14:06.000 --> 14:06.730
Call me Tang.

14:06.740 --> 14:09.260
Barbecue pork buns are here.

14:10.840 --> 14:12.080
Honey, what are these called?

14:12.080 --> 14:14.510
These are barbecue pork buns.

14:14.660 --> 14:16.440
-Barbecue pork buns?
-Barbecue pork buns?

14:16.440 --> 14:18.270
A famous snack in Shengcheng.

14:18.720 --> 14:19.750
Hey, Fen, Fen.

14:19.910 --> 14:20.910
Give one to him.

14:21.030 --> 14:21.870
Have him try this.

14:21.870 --> 14:22.530
Okay, okay.

14:22.670 --> 14:24.310
I see that today's dishes

14:24.550 --> 14:26.080
were all made by the ladies.

14:26.120 --> 14:26.840
We men

14:26.960 --> 14:28.270
can't just sit back and enjoy it.

14:28.270 --> 14:28.810
In a bit,

14:28.870 --> 14:30.800
I'll volunteer to wash the dishes.

14:31.840 --> 14:33.080
Look. Just look at that.

14:33.080 --> 14:33.480
Yong,

14:33.630 --> 14:34.570
learn from him.

14:34.720 --> 14:35.480
Okay, okay.

14:35.480 --> 14:36.670
I-I'll wash the dishes too.

14:36.670 --> 14:37.870
Try it while it's hot.

14:38.670 --> 14:39.790
Let's try it.

14:40.200 --> 14:41.140
Have a taste, come on.

14:41.140 --> 14:42.360
Try it, come on.

14:43.050 --> 14:44.170
Are you not leaving

14:44.200 --> 14:45.270
tonight?

14:47.270 --> 14:48.440
If you put it that way,

14:48.440 --> 14:49.270
I'll be shameless

14:49.270 --> 14:50.670
and stay here tonight.

14:52.870 --> 14:53.390
Fen.

14:53.790 --> 14:54.520
Is that okay?

14:56.030 --> 14:56.390
Um...

14:56.510 --> 14:57.000
Well...

14:57.360 --> 14:58.790
I'll go add some soup for everyone.

14:58.790 --> 14:59.120
Okay,

14:59.240 --> 14:59.750
I'll help you.

14:59.750 --> 15:00.550
It's a bit hot.

15:00.790 --> 15:01.120
Well...

15:01.120 --> 15:01.440
Let me do it. Let me.

15:01.440 --> 15:02.100
Let me do it.

15:02.440 --> 15:02.870
Let me.

15:04.310 --> 15:04.970
Okay, okay.

15:05.240 --> 15:05.750
Well...

15:05.750 --> 15:06.410
Okay, okay.

15:08.290 --> 15:09.220
What's going on?

15:10.680 --> 15:11.340
What's happening?

15:11.340 --> 15:12.740
Help me lift the curtain.

15:12.910 --> 15:13.710
Okay, thanks.

15:14.440 --> 15:15.770
Fengmei, add some soup.

15:16.590 --> 15:17.200
Granny Yu,

15:17.960 --> 15:19.540
when did those two

15:19.570 --> 15:20.790
get to this stage?

15:22.960 --> 15:25.000
There's a lot you don't know.

15:28.200 --> 15:29.720
That man seems

15:29.740 --> 15:31.070
to be interested in Fen.

15:31.320 --> 15:32.110
No way.

15:32.790 --> 15:34.270
They don't look like a match.

15:34.270 --> 15:35.030
Eat. Eat.

15:35.200 --> 15:35.750
D-D-Don't...

15:35.750 --> 15:36.870
Don't gossip.

15:36.890 --> 15:37.720
Drink up, come on.

15:37.720 --> 15:38.910
-Come on.
-Come on.

15:39.320 --> 15:40.000
Have a drink.

15:40.000 --> 15:40.330
Okay.

15:40.550 --> 15:40.880
Okay.

15:43.200 --> 15:43.930
I'm leaving, Yong!

15:43.930 --> 15:44.620
Bye, Yong!

15:45.080 --> 15:46.360
Bye. Happy New Year.

15:46.720 --> 15:47.550
Come visit often.

15:47.550 --> 15:48.210
Come visit.

15:48.600 --> 15:49.630
Okay. Take care.

15:52.000 --> 15:52.750
Comrade Tang.

15:52.750 --> 15:53.390
Thank you.

15:53.440 --> 15:54.630
Treat this place like your own home.

15:54.630 --> 15:55.150
Will do.

15:55.480 --> 15:56.120
Take care.

15:56.270 --> 15:56.930
Be careful.

15:57.240 --> 15:58.100
Happy New Year.

15:58.440 --> 15:58.960
Happy New Year.

15:58.960 --> 16:00.160
Take care. Take care.

16:05.080 --> 16:06.010
Comrade Liu Fen.

16:08.390 --> 16:09.710
I'd like to have a word with you,

16:09.710 --> 16:10.280
if I may.

16:15.750 --> 16:17.480
I'll get straight to the point.

16:17.720 --> 16:18.550
We've known

16:18.750 --> 16:19.240
each other

16:19.240 --> 16:20.500
for almost half a year.

16:21.150 --> 16:21.910
I think,

16:22.240 --> 16:23.750
in our personality

16:24.360 --> 16:25.000
and age,

16:26.390 --> 16:27.450
we're compatible.

16:28.440 --> 16:29.500
Most importantly,

16:29.840 --> 16:31.000
we are still single.

16:32.240 --> 16:33.150
Let's date

16:33.320 --> 16:35.150
seriously,

16:35.440 --> 16:36.900
with the marriage in mind.

16:41.420 --> 16:42.480
What do you think?

16:44.240 --> 16:45.510
So people in this era

16:45.940 --> 16:47.350
can also be so direct.

16:48.120 --> 16:49.850
This directness isn't uncool;

16:50.510 --> 16:54.390
instead, it feels brave and sincere.

16:55.150 --> 16:55.960
Perhaps,

16:56.720 --> 16:59.320
avoidance is the worst choice.

16:59.670 --> 17:00.330
Mayor Tang.

17:01.800 --> 17:03.080
No, Mr. Tang.

17:03.480 --> 17:04.480
Just call me Tang.

17:05.109 --> 17:05.589
Okay.

17:06.920 --> 17:08.270
Fen,

17:08.640 --> 17:09.339
Xiaolan,

17:09.589 --> 17:10.750
and me,

17:11.030 --> 17:12.349
we are very grateful

17:13.069 --> 17:14.640
for your care in Shengcheng.

17:14.640 --> 17:16.099
Let's not talk about that.

17:16.109 --> 17:16.829
But I...

17:17.880 --> 17:18.940
have something...

17:19.829 --> 17:20.200
Yong.

17:21.510 --> 17:22.310
Do you think

17:22.680 --> 17:23.790
it's wrong for me

17:24.109 --> 17:25.270
to date your sister Liu Fen

17:25.270 --> 17:26.329
with the intention

17:26.859 --> 17:27.790
of marrying her?

17:30.160 --> 17:31.560
I-I didn't mean...

17:31.590 --> 17:32.240
Mr. Tang.

17:33.640 --> 17:34.310
I'd like to

17:35.110 --> 17:36.570
have a word with you alone.

17:36.960 --> 17:37.400
Sure.

17:37.790 --> 17:38.850
Let's go for a walk.

17:39.000 --> 17:39.330
Okay.

17:39.420 --> 17:40.420
We'll take a walk.

17:48.810 --> 17:50.540
There's nothing wrong with it,

17:52.160 --> 17:54.290
but it feels like everything is wrong.

18:01.830 --> 18:02.960
Oh my goodness.

18:03.880 --> 18:06.440
New Year in the countryside is so lively.

18:08.550 --> 18:10.160
Cooking a whole table of food

18:10.160 --> 18:11.480
made me exhausted.

18:13.480 --> 18:14.480
Thanks for your hard work, Granny Yu.

18:14.480 --> 18:14.820
Here.

18:15.000 --> 18:15.930
Have some water.

18:16.400 --> 18:17.800
We were all working hard.

18:21.960 --> 18:22.560
Granny Yu.

18:23.200 --> 18:24.110
Why didn't you

18:24.110 --> 18:25.170
tell me in advance?

18:25.640 --> 18:26.900
If I had told you first,

18:27.200 --> 18:28.800
would it have worked so well?

18:30.030 --> 18:32.070
Aren't the neighbors all watching

18:32.070 --> 18:33.270
to see what kind of man

18:33.400 --> 18:35.000
your mom will find?

18:35.590 --> 18:36.720
Now they've seen it.

18:37.160 --> 18:38.160
That shut them up.

18:41.110 --> 18:42.680
But I think my mom

18:43.030 --> 18:44.890
might not be able to accept it yet.

18:45.750 --> 18:47.510
You've done enough

18:47.510 --> 18:49.070
to make your mom proud.

18:49.680 --> 18:50.510
As for

18:51.720 --> 18:53.110
the inferiority caused

18:53.920 --> 18:55.070
by her divorce,

18:55.750 --> 18:56.200
no one else

18:56.200 --> 18:57.790
can help her.

18:59.400 --> 19:01.130
She must walk out of it herself.

19:01.900 --> 19:03.200
Now that

19:03.200 --> 19:05.000
such an excellent man likes her,

19:06.160 --> 19:07.960
even if they don't work out,

19:08.730 --> 19:09.990
at least in the future,

19:10.740 --> 19:12.970
your mom's standards

19:13.400 --> 19:16.070
will be higher, right?

19:18.070 --> 19:19.240
I can't argue

19:19.240 --> 19:20.640
with what Granny Yu said.

19:20.880 --> 19:22.310
Even in 30 years,

19:23.440 --> 19:26.570
there will still be people
in society who think this way:

19:26.830 --> 19:27.750
For a woman,

19:28.110 --> 19:30.310
no matter how successful her career is,

19:30.720 --> 19:32.320
or how wonderful her life is,

19:32.510 --> 19:34.240
if she doesn't have a marriage,

19:34.310 --> 19:35.590
her life is still considered incomplete.

19:35.590 --> 19:36.680
You are so kind

19:37.400 --> 19:39.260
to invite me over for the New Year.

19:39.270 --> 19:41.000
I couldn't come empty-handed.

19:41.800 --> 19:42.480
Consider this

19:42.480 --> 19:44.350
my New Year's gift to you.

19:46.030 --> 19:47.350
Whether my mom can accept it

19:47.350 --> 19:48.410
is not certain yet,

19:49.110 --> 19:50.480
but I understand your intentions,

19:50.480 --> 19:51.200
Granny Yu.

19:51.880 --> 19:53.080
Thank you, Granny Yu.

19:54.400 --> 19:56.200
I didn't bring you a gift,

19:56.600 --> 19:57.930
yet you're thanking me?

19:58.870 --> 20:00.800
Well, you are Granny Yu, after all.

20:03.110 --> 20:04.030
Fen, you're back.

20:04.030 --> 20:04.560
I'm back.

20:08.000 --> 20:08.720
Mr. Tang.

20:10.270 --> 20:11.200
I have never met

20:11.200 --> 20:12.460
a leader as good as you.

20:14.480 --> 20:15.720
But you are a leader,

20:16.350 --> 20:17.350
who are educated,

20:18.030 --> 20:18.750
unlike me.

20:19.920 --> 20:21.030
I was born in this village

20:21.030 --> 20:22.290
and grew up right here.

20:22.350 --> 20:23.610
I'm not very educated.

20:25.920 --> 20:27.030
So I think...

20:29.750 --> 20:31.440
there is a big gap between us.

20:32.920 --> 20:33.880
You and I...

20:35.070 --> 20:35.930
aren't really—

20:39.350 --> 20:40.480
Did you catch a cold?

20:41.790 --> 20:43.030
Button up your coat.

20:52.550 --> 20:53.280
Button it up.

20:57.640 --> 20:59.640
You didn't wear long johns, did you?

21:02.030 --> 21:03.830
The village isn't like the city.

21:04.200 --> 21:06.350
There are no tall buildings
to block the wind.

21:06.350 --> 21:08.440
It's several degrees colder
than in the city.

21:08.440 --> 21:09.170
Coming here,

21:09.920 --> 21:10.920
surely in many ways,

21:10.920 --> 21:12.120
you are not used to it.

21:15.110 --> 21:16.350
But I think this place

21:17.030 --> 21:17.690
has good air

21:19.000 --> 21:20.000
and good scenery.

21:20.790 --> 21:21.590
What's more,

21:22.030 --> 21:23.830
the people raised in the village

21:23.880 --> 21:24.810
are even better.

21:27.770 --> 21:29.430
Light one. Quick. Fireworks.

21:30.830 --> 21:32.490
Come on, let's do it together.

21:38.030 --> 21:38.560
Hey, kid.

21:39.750 --> 21:40.810
Can you give me two?

21:41.120 --> 21:41.970
Sure, here.

21:42.000 --> 21:42.400
Okay.

21:42.550 --> 21:42.920
Here.

21:43.480 --> 21:43.940
Thanks.

21:44.960 --> 21:46.070
Let's go play over there.

21:46.070 --> 21:46.350
Okay.

21:46.350 --> 21:47.010
Be careful.

21:49.440 --> 21:50.500
I'll light one too.

21:52.000 --> 21:53.590
I used to do this when I was little.

21:53.590 --> 21:54.850
It's been so many years

21:54.920 --> 21:56.320
since I played with this.

22:04.400 --> 22:05.330
It's beautiful.

22:06.640 --> 22:08.170
Do you want to light one too?

22:20.680 --> 22:21.550
Be careful.

22:36.480 --> 22:37.000
Xia.

22:37.750 --> 22:39.480
I hustled a job managing costumes,

22:39.480 --> 22:40.610
and I got backstage.

22:41.830 --> 22:43.720
Only after I got here did I realize

22:43.880 --> 22:45.030
that the hosts'

22:45.030 --> 22:46.030
and the guests' costumes

22:46.030 --> 22:47.960
had already been decided long ago.

22:48.510 --> 22:50.680
I'm afraid it's going to be difficult
this time.

22:50.680 --> 22:52.110
Don't rush to admit defeat.

22:52.110 --> 22:53.030
You already made it backstage.

22:53.030 --> 22:54.510
That's half the battle won.

22:54.510 --> 22:56.480
As for the hosts' and guests' outfits,

22:56.480 --> 22:57.960
is it certain they won't change them?

22:57.960 --> 22:58.720
Even if they're decided,

22:58.720 --> 23:00.350
couldn't something go wrong later?

23:00.350 --> 23:01.680
If there's no opportunity,

23:01.680 --> 23:03.160
you have to find one.

23:04.790 --> 23:05.510
Xia,

23:06.350 --> 23:07.750
you mean...

23:08.070 --> 23:09.480
I think you can try

23:09.640 --> 23:11.110
focusing on the artists from Gangdao.

23:11.110 --> 23:12.680
They might have more freedom

23:12.680 --> 23:14.540
with their own clothing choices.

23:15.160 --> 23:17.220
For instance, someone like Wu Kaili.

23:17.270 --> 23:17.960
Wu Kaili?

23:18.240 --> 23:18.640
Yes.

23:19.510 --> 23:20.960
Alright. Good luck.

23:21.350 --> 23:21.750
Xia.

23:26.030 --> 23:27.090
Done making calls?

23:29.240 --> 23:30.170
Missing anyone?

23:32.110 --> 23:32.590
No.

23:34.440 --> 23:34.790
Good.

23:43.470 --> 23:44.670
I didn't miss anyone.

23:45.590 --> 23:47.920
I just haven't figured out
what to say yet.

23:50.110 --> 23:52.480
Hot dumplings are here!

23:52.480 --> 23:53.270
Fengmei, sit down quickly.

23:53.270 --> 23:54.350
The dumplings are ready.

23:54.350 --> 23:55.640
Come on, come on. Let's eat together.

23:55.640 --> 23:56.320
Let's all

23:56.350 --> 23:57.510
wish Granny Yu good health.

23:57.510 --> 23:57.830
Okay.

23:57.830 --> 23:58.640
-Okay?
-Okay.

23:58.720 --> 24:00.680
And wish everyone a Happy New Year.

24:00.710 --> 24:03.790
-Happy New Year!
-May joy fill our home!

24:07.070 --> 24:07.870
Here, Liu Fen.

24:08.440 --> 24:09.040
Fen, here.

24:09.440 --> 24:11.300
Let me give you a piece of chicken.

24:12.350 --> 24:13.410
Eat while it's hot.

24:14.790 --> 24:15.720
Have a dumpling then.

24:15.720 --> 24:17.240
Yes, you'd better eat it while it's hot.

24:17.240 --> 24:17.640
Look.

24:18.030 --> 24:18.960
Let me serve you.

24:21.350 --> 24:21.880
Fengmei.

24:22.240 --> 24:22.790
Have a dumpling.

24:22.790 --> 24:23.450
Okay, okay.

24:23.980 --> 24:25.220
Mr. Tang, please eat.

24:25.350 --> 24:25.750
Try it.

24:26.070 --> 24:26.670
Thank you.

24:26.830 --> 24:27.790
Just help yourself.

24:27.790 --> 24:28.920
Just help yourself.

24:30.640 --> 24:31.240
Granny Yu.

24:31.510 --> 24:33.910
I see you were rejected
by Fen, weren't you?

24:34.240 --> 24:35.970
It wasn't exactly a rejection.

24:36.960 --> 24:38.200
Fen just thinks

24:38.200 --> 24:39.750
that the two of us

24:40.350 --> 24:42.410
aren't very suitable for each other.

24:43.070 --> 24:43.720
She...

24:47.270 --> 24:48.480
I still want to thank you

24:48.480 --> 24:49.350
for calling me.

24:51.480 --> 24:53.140
That's because you have guts.

24:53.270 --> 24:53.870
Thank you.

24:54.350 --> 24:55.160
Keep trying.

24:55.830 --> 24:56.270
I will.

24:58.960 --> 24:59.490
Xiaolan.

25:03.920 --> 25:05.110
Dear friends,

25:05.440 --> 25:06.200
comrades,

25:06.440 --> 25:08.160
the Year of the Snake Spring Festival Gala

25:08.160 --> 25:10.750
officially begins now.

25:13.510 --> 25:14.880
As we bid farewell to the old
and welcome the new,

25:14.880 --> 25:15.640
in this wonderful moment,

25:15.640 --> 25:16.960
we gather here happily.

25:16.960 --> 25:17.490
Xiaolan,

25:17.920 --> 25:18.920
they aren't using

25:18.920 --> 25:19.920
our Luna clothes.

25:20.110 --> 25:21.510
Don't worry. It has just started.

25:21.510 --> 25:22.440
Let's eat first.

25:22.640 --> 25:23.030
Right, right.

25:23.030 --> 25:23.720
They'll definitely be there.

25:23.720 --> 25:24.270
Let's have another drink.

25:24.270 --> 25:24.750
Let's toast to Granny Yu again.

25:24.750 --> 25:25.590
Wish Granny Yu good health

25:25.590 --> 25:26.400
and a long life.

25:26.400 --> 25:27.000
Great.

25:27.750 --> 25:30.200
-Happy New Year!
-Happy New Year!

26:01.670 --> 26:02.350
Wei.

26:02.920 --> 26:03.780
Where is Cheng?

26:04.590 --> 26:05.440
Happy New Year.

26:05.440 --> 26:06.030
Happy New Year.

26:06.030 --> 26:06.640
Cheng.

26:07.550 --> 26:08.070
Cheng.

26:08.340 --> 26:09.510
Come back for dumplings.

26:09.510 --> 26:09.920
Okay.

26:13.750 --> 26:15.160
Fish is here.

26:19.310 --> 26:20.030
Grandma,

26:20.240 --> 26:22.080
you look so beautiful.

26:22.110 --> 26:24.200
You are never serious.

26:24.640 --> 26:25.590
Tell me,

26:25.920 --> 26:26.550
next year,

26:26.830 --> 26:28.200
can you find a boyfriend

26:28.200 --> 26:29.160
and bring him home for the New Year?

26:29.160 --> 26:30.070
Grandma.

26:30.070 --> 26:31.240
Okay, okay.

26:31.640 --> 26:32.640
No problem.

26:32.880 --> 26:34.310
No problem.

26:45.480 --> 26:46.030
One more?

26:46.160 --> 26:46.510
Okay.

26:47.840 --> 26:48.690
These two

26:48.720 --> 26:50.450
rarely see each other all year.

26:50.910 --> 26:51.720
We still need to find a way

26:51.720 --> 26:53.380
to move to Shengcheng sooner.

26:53.640 --> 26:54.350
A family

26:54.510 --> 26:55.680
living happily together

26:55.680 --> 26:57.080
is what life is all about.

26:59.260 --> 27:01.160
My brother has mentioned it
to me several times.

27:01.160 --> 27:03.270
He said once he was done
with his current project

27:03.270 --> 27:04.270
and made some more money,

27:04.270 --> 27:05.600
he'd bring you two over.

27:06.310 --> 27:07.440
To be honest,

27:07.830 --> 27:08.720
I really can't bear to leave

27:08.720 --> 27:10.160
the business in Jingcheng.

27:10.160 --> 27:11.270
If we close the shop,

27:11.270 --> 27:13.600
think of how much money
we'd lose in a year.

27:14.160 --> 27:15.640
I want to stick it out
for a couple of years.

27:15.640 --> 27:16.830
After we save enough money

27:16.830 --> 27:18.220
and are better off.

27:18.750 --> 27:19.750
Before long,

27:19.920 --> 27:21.200
buying a commercial residential property
in Shengcheng

27:21.200 --> 27:22.480
will let us
get the local household registration.

27:22.480 --> 27:24.200
By then, it'll be convenient for Tao

27:24.200 --> 27:24.700
to go there to study,

27:24.700 --> 27:25.960
without the need for temporary schooling.

27:25.960 --> 27:26.640
Buy a house?

27:27.240 --> 27:29.000
Don't work units allocate one?

27:29.030 --> 27:30.000
Why buy a house?

27:30.190 --> 27:31.450
Do you have a work unit?

27:32.320 --> 27:32.830
No.

27:32.830 --> 27:34.400
People like us without work units

27:34.400 --> 27:35.460
have to buy our own.

27:37.240 --> 27:38.160
Comrade Liu Fen,

27:38.160 --> 27:40.090
you are getting more enlightened.

27:40.680 --> 27:41.540
How about this?

27:41.750 --> 27:43.160
Give me some more time.

27:43.640 --> 27:44.710
I'll buy the land

27:44.920 --> 27:46.030
and build the house myself.

27:46.030 --> 27:47.000
I'll keep one floor

27:47.000 --> 27:48.270
for our family to live in.

27:48.270 --> 27:49.200
Xiaolan,

27:49.220 --> 27:50.520
you are so capable.

27:50.550 --> 27:52.070
We're waiting for your big mansion.

27:52.070 --> 27:52.590
Here.

27:55.240 --> 27:55.960
Xiaolan!

27:56.270 --> 27:57.000
Your call!

27:57.220 --> 27:57.880
Coming!

28:01.550 --> 28:01.950
Hello?

28:02.550 --> 28:03.030
Xia.

28:03.480 --> 28:04.350
Is the TV on?

28:05.680 --> 28:06.480
Watch it, quick.

28:06.480 --> 28:07.080
It worked.

28:07.960 --> 28:09.280
Mom, Mom!

28:09.350 --> 28:10.590
Auntie, come look!

28:12.920 --> 28:13.720
Is this it?

28:14.800 --> 28:15.720
What Wu Kaili is wearing

28:15.720 --> 28:17.270
is our Luna clothes!

28:17.270 --> 28:18.160
-Yes, right.
-Really?

28:18.160 --> 28:18.680
Isn't that

28:18.680 --> 28:19.920
the singer from Gangdao?

28:19.920 --> 28:20.320
She...

28:20.440 --> 28:22.070
She's wearing Luna clothes!

28:22.070 --> 28:23.480
This is Xiaolan's brand!

28:23.880 --> 28:24.310
Yes.

28:24.680 --> 28:25.680
That's great.

28:25.680 --> 28:26.080
Right?

28:26.200 --> 28:26.920
Chen,

28:27.170 --> 28:27.960
how did you make it?

28:27.960 --> 28:29.020
That's so amazing.

28:29.720 --> 28:31.110
You have no idea, Xia.

28:31.550 --> 28:32.590
Wu Kaili's clothes

28:32.590 --> 28:33.920
were prepared long ago.

28:34.350 --> 28:36.150
I kept watching her for a chance.

28:36.310 --> 28:37.680
I was about to give up.

28:38.240 --> 28:40.110
Then I finally found her costume.

28:38.490 --> 28:41.290
[One hour ago]

28:51.350 --> 28:52.590
One look and I knew,

28:53.550 --> 28:54.350
my chance had come.

28:54.190 --> 28:55.670
[Wu Kaili]

28:55.510 --> 28:57.920
This dress is the exact same color
as the background.

28:55.890 --> 29:00.530
[Dressing Room]

28:58.170 --> 28:58.920
Once she's on stage,

28:58.920 --> 29:00.980
will the audience even see our Kaili?

29:01.080 --> 29:01.790
Sorry.

29:02.400 --> 29:03.400
I'm really sorry.

29:03.400 --> 29:04.480
Sorry won't cut it.

29:04.750 --> 29:06.240
We need a solution.

29:06.240 --> 29:06.920
I'll think of one right now.

29:06.920 --> 29:08.640
Hurry, hurry!

29:10.000 --> 29:11.110
So annoying!

29:11.400 --> 29:12.200
What do we do now?

29:12.200 --> 29:13.400
Let them go look.

29:15.350 --> 29:16.030
Who is it?

29:18.070 --> 29:19.280
Excuse me.

29:19.310 --> 29:19.750
Hello.

29:19.830 --> 29:20.400
Miss Wu.

29:20.920 --> 29:22.040
Do you need something?

29:22.040 --> 29:23.720
I am the General Manager
of Luna Womenswear,

29:23.720 --> 29:24.520
Chen Xiliang.

29:27.310 --> 29:27.790
Miss Wu.

29:30.200 --> 29:31.010
Please calm down.

29:31.010 --> 29:31.590
It's like this.

29:31.590 --> 29:32.770
When I passed by just now,

29:32.770 --> 29:34.070
I accidentally overheard
your conversation.

29:34.070 --> 29:36.070
Is there a problem with the costume?

29:37.790 --> 29:38.480
This is our

29:38.480 --> 29:39.750
Luna brand sample.

29:40.070 --> 29:42.400
It just so happens these clothes are here.

29:42.420 --> 29:43.080
Since I have

29:43.320 --> 29:44.970
heard so much about Miss Wu,

29:45.030 --> 29:46.310
I'd like to offer her

29:46.310 --> 29:47.240
these clothes for free

29:47.240 --> 29:48.700
as performance costumes.

29:51.400 --> 29:52.200
Rest assured,

29:52.350 --> 29:53.000
these clothes

29:53.000 --> 29:54.550
are new arrivals not yet on the market.

29:54.550 --> 29:56.410
Very suitable for today's stage.

29:59.000 --> 29:59.560
Miss Wu,

29:59.680 --> 30:01.740
you can take a look at the style first.

30:10.270 --> 30:10.920
Thanks to you, Xia.

30:10.920 --> 30:12.120
Your words woke me up.

30:12.480 --> 30:14.110
Wu Kaili really was an opportunity.

30:14.110 --> 30:15.310
You're really smart.

30:15.680 --> 30:17.510
Xia, don't be modest.

30:17.960 --> 30:19.510
Without your on-the-spot execution,

30:19.510 --> 30:21.310
all my talk would have been for nothing.

30:21.310 --> 30:22.610
With this wind, Luna

30:22.640 --> 30:23.920
can skyrocket.

30:24.870 --> 30:25.310
Alright.

30:25.310 --> 30:26.510
Happy New Year, Chen.

30:26.510 --> 30:27.640
Happy New Year, Xia.

30:28.920 --> 30:30.880
W-We're going to be rich!

30:33.480 --> 30:34.000
Silly!

30:34.000 --> 30:34.800
That's great!

30:35.890 --> 30:37.200
Silly!

30:37.880 --> 30:38.940
Congratulations.

30:40.590 --> 30:41.720
Chen Xiliang is indeed

30:41.720 --> 30:42.650
a future tycoon.

30:43.160 --> 30:45.290
No matter how challenging the task is,

30:45.310 --> 30:47.370
he dares to burn his bridges and do it.

30:47.960 --> 30:48.960
Fearlessness

30:49.400 --> 30:50.660
is his Midas touch.

30:51.160 --> 30:52.270
He is a true pioneer

30:52.270 --> 30:53.590
of this era.

30:54.030 --> 30:55.920
Dear viewers,

30:56.240 --> 30:57.150
the New Year's bell

30:57.150 --> 30:58.750
is about to ring.

30:59.200 --> 31:00.790
-Let's look forward to it.
-Five!

31:00.790 --> 31:02.790
-Let's count down together.
-Four!

31:03.840 --> 31:04.980
-Three!
-Three!

31:06.190 --> 31:07.330
-Two!
-Two!

31:08.940 --> 31:09.860
-One!
-One!

31:32.290 --> 31:40.630
♪ Unforgettable tonight,
unforgettable tonight ♪

31:40.650 --> 31:48.910
♪ Though far apart,
we're under the same sky ♪

31:49.120 --> 31:57.960
♪ Across our great land,
we hold each other tight ♪

31:57.990 --> 32:05.970
♪ Let's wish our motherland bright,
our motherland bright ♪

32:00.310 --> 32:01.160
Back for the New Year?

32:01.160 --> 32:02.160
It's the New Year.

32:02.440 --> 32:03.640
Back for the New Year.

32:04.400 --> 32:05.110
Just got back.

32:05.110 --> 32:07.640
We're going to pay respects
to our ancestors.

32:07.960 --> 32:08.760
I'll carry it.

32:10.750 --> 32:11.590
Let me carry it. Come on.

32:11.590 --> 32:12.790
No need. It's just a shovel.

32:12.790 --> 32:13.920
It's not that heavy.

32:15.030 --> 32:15.830
Actually,

32:17.030 --> 32:18.360
you didn't have to come.

32:20.960 --> 32:21.720
If I hadn't,

32:22.000 --> 32:22.720
I'd feel bad

32:22.720 --> 32:23.980
staying at your place.

32:25.440 --> 32:26.110
In fact,

32:26.410 --> 32:27.920
you don't need to overthink it.

32:27.920 --> 32:29.450
As just an ordinary friend,

32:29.480 --> 32:31.680
it's only right

32:33.720 --> 32:35.920
that I come along for ancestor worship.

32:36.680 --> 32:37.750
Let me do it. I'll sweep.

32:37.750 --> 32:38.950
It's okay. I'll do it.

32:41.550 --> 32:42.160
Mom, Dad,

32:42.790 --> 32:43.790
our whole family

32:43.950 --> 32:45.030
is here to see you.

32:45.680 --> 32:46.240
Mom, Dad,

32:46.920 --> 32:48.000
Tao is doing well.

32:48.450 --> 32:50.350
Xiaolan is leading our whole family
to prosperity.

32:50.350 --> 32:51.640
We're living a good life now.

32:51.640 --> 32:52.840
Please rest assured.

32:53.880 --> 32:54.510
Mom, Dad.

33:00.680 --> 33:01.880
Liu Fen's dad and mom.

33:02.510 --> 33:03.710
Nice to meet you both.

33:04.510 --> 33:05.840
My name is Tang Hong'en.

33:06.160 --> 33:08.440
I am honored to visit you today.

33:09.790 --> 33:10.440
Actually,

33:10.960 --> 33:12.030
it is quite a pity

33:13.270 --> 33:14.440
that I never met you.

33:16.480 --> 33:17.880
But you can rest assured.

33:18.300 --> 33:19.860
Liu Fen and Xiaolan

33:20.110 --> 33:21.510
are living very well now.

33:22.550 --> 33:24.010
I can also promise you both

33:24.590 --> 33:25.650
that in the future,

33:25.680 --> 33:27.210
they will live even better.

33:28.440 --> 33:29.100
From now on,

33:29.960 --> 33:31.960
I will come to pay my respects often.

33:34.640 --> 33:35.070
Okay.

33:36.270 --> 33:37.800
Let's kowtow to Mom and Dad.

33:53.290 --> 33:55.800
[Tomb of Late Father Liu Dianzong
and Late Mother Chen Shulan]

33:54.110 --> 33:54.640
Let's go.

33:59.700 --> 34:00.550
Wait a moment.

34:04.290 --> 34:05.770
Mr. Tang is really brave.

34:07.710 --> 34:08.239
Let's go.

34:08.320 --> 34:08.850
Let's go.

34:18.719 --> 34:19.380
Don't move.

34:19.920 --> 34:20.580
Let me do it.

34:21.409 --> 34:22.409
Put on the gloves.

34:22.550 --> 34:23.610
It's fine. No need.

34:25.510 --> 34:26.170
Stand back.

34:35.480 --> 34:36.920
Better than you.

34:38.690 --> 34:40.290
You don't need to stand here.

34:42.320 --> 34:43.850
Just put my clothes inside.

34:44.010 --> 34:44.560
Leave it.

34:44.590 --> 34:45.670
Put on the gloves.

34:50.030 --> 34:51.429
When you see them dating,

34:51.800 --> 34:53.150
how do you feel?

35:02.630 --> 35:04.030
Let me do it. Give it to me.

35:22.360 --> 35:23.120
Don't move.

35:23.150 --> 35:24.410
It's too heavy for you.

35:24.440 --> 35:25.170
Give it to me.

35:28.320 --> 35:28.760
Well...

35:28.760 --> 35:29.880
Sweep the floor again.

35:29.880 --> 35:30.440
Sweep the yard.

35:30.440 --> 35:31.960
It's quite dirty. Right.

35:42.920 --> 35:43.670
Are you okay?

35:43.920 --> 35:44.450
I'm fine.

35:44.710 --> 35:45.440
Your face.

35:45.600 --> 35:46.190
What's wrong?

35:46.190 --> 35:46.760
Mayor.

35:47.410 --> 35:48.200
Well...

35:48.230 --> 35:49.000
Is it lit?

35:49.510 --> 35:50.800
It's definitely lit.

35:50.920 --> 35:51.670
But the smoke

35:51.760 --> 35:52.690
is a bit too much.

35:53.070 --> 35:53.800
It's okay.

35:55.060 --> 35:56.940
Wipe the Mayor's face.

35:58.080 --> 35:58.680
Thank you.

35:59.110 --> 36:01.360
How long do you plan to stay at our house?

36:03.000 --> 36:05.030
As long as he wants.

36:05.220 --> 36:06.560
We have plenty of room.

36:06.590 --> 36:07.530
I didn't mean anything by it.

36:07.530 --> 36:08.660
Stay a few more days.

36:09.230 --> 36:10.960
Just don't burn the house down.

36:11.280 --> 36:11.760
I wouldn't do that.

36:11.760 --> 36:12.480
Thank you. Thank you, Fengmei.

36:12.480 --> 36:13.540
As long as it's lit.

36:13.800 --> 36:14.400
It's fine.

36:14.510 --> 36:16.230
It's cold. Put on your coat.

36:16.590 --> 36:17.150
Put on the padded jacket.

36:17.150 --> 36:17.960
Okay, okay.

36:18.440 --> 36:19.300
I'll handle it.

36:19.510 --> 36:20.710
It's okay. It's okay.

36:24.110 --> 36:25.230
Smile. Tao, smile.

36:25.440 --> 36:26.960
Ready? Three, two, one.

36:27.150 --> 36:27.630
Cheese.

36:28.190 --> 36:28.590
Okay, done.

36:28.590 --> 36:29.760
Come on, I'll take one for you.

36:29.760 --> 36:30.280
Come on, come on.

36:30.280 --> 36:31.070
Right, right.

36:31.070 --> 36:31.470
Hurry.

36:31.630 --> 36:32.320
Granny Yu.

36:32.430 --> 36:33.150
Let's take one together.

36:33.150 --> 36:35.210
Come on, let's take a photo together.

36:35.880 --> 36:37.630
Come on, smile.

36:38.110 --> 36:40.400
One, two, three.

36:43.520 --> 36:45.040
May I take a photo

36:45.120 --> 36:46.190
with Comrade Liu Fen

36:46.190 --> 36:46.990
as a keepsake?

36:48.880 --> 36:49.280
Sure.

36:51.430 --> 36:52.760
Xiaolan, take it for us.

36:53.060 --> 36:53.840
Sure, no problem.

36:53.840 --> 36:54.320
Come on.

36:55.230 --> 36:55.830
Over here.

36:56.400 --> 36:56.760
Okay.

36:58.960 --> 37:00.190
Mom, smile.

37:01.360 --> 37:01.960
Here we go.

37:02.280 --> 37:03.800
Three, two, one.

37:05.230 --> 37:05.590
Done.

37:05.610 --> 37:06.960
Okay, let's take one together.

37:06.960 --> 37:08.030
Right, together.

37:08.030 --> 37:08.630
Together.

37:08.880 --> 37:09.320
Get in position first.

37:09.320 --> 37:11.180
Come on, Granny Yu. That's right.

37:12.400 --> 37:13.800
Don't shake the camera.

37:13.880 --> 37:14.670
Just hold it steady.

37:14.670 --> 37:15.400
Hold it steady.

37:15.400 --> 37:17.400
Don't make it blurry like last time.

37:18.320 --> 37:20.180
What a beautiful fireworks show!

37:21.930 --> 37:22.710
It's so beautiful.

37:22.710 --> 37:23.710
It looks amazing.

37:28.710 --> 37:29.480
Who set these off?

37:29.480 --> 37:30.610
Let's go take a look.

37:32.430 --> 37:33.090
Zhou Cheng.

38:18.630 --> 38:19.880
What are you doing here?

38:19.880 --> 38:20.740
Happy New Year,

38:21.000 --> 38:21.530
Xiaolan.

38:23.590 --> 38:24.450
Happy New Year.

38:25.360 --> 38:26.020
Zhou Cheng!

38:26.360 --> 38:27.280
Come on. Together.

38:27.280 --> 38:28.630
Let's take a group photo.

38:28.630 --> 38:29.030
Uncle.

38:29.150 --> 38:29.550
Hurry.

38:29.550 --> 38:31.550
Let's take a family photo together.

38:31.590 --> 38:32.450
Happy New Year.

38:32.750 --> 38:33.710
Happy New Year.

38:33.710 --> 38:34.150
Yong.

38:34.150 --> 38:34.800
Come here. Come here.

38:34.800 --> 38:36.760
Take a photo of our family.

38:38.710 --> 38:39.320
Come on.

38:39.640 --> 38:41.230
Granny Yu, stand in the middle.

38:41.230 --> 38:42.280
-Granny Yu.
-Yes.

38:42.760 --> 38:43.190
Tao, over here.

38:43.190 --> 38:43.990
Come quickly.

38:44.360 --> 38:45.630
I've set it all up for you.

38:45.630 --> 38:46.760
Just press this in a moment,

38:46.760 --> 38:47.560
and that's it.

38:47.590 --> 38:48.320
I know how. I know.

38:48.320 --> 38:49.720
Are you sure you know how?

38:50.150 --> 38:50.680
I'm sure.

38:51.150 --> 38:51.880
Ready?

38:51.880 --> 38:52.280
Ready.

38:52.280 --> 38:52.630
Okay.

38:52.670 --> 38:53.760
Wait. I'll give the cue.

38:53.760 --> 38:55.230
Everyone, one, two, three.

38:55.230 --> 38:57.880
-Happy New Year!
-Happy New Year!

39:03.510 --> 39:04.150
Honestly,

39:04.800 --> 39:05.760
when I first walked in,

39:05.760 --> 39:07.670
I didn't even recognize Mayor Tang.

39:07.670 --> 39:09.470
I thought he was just a neighbor.

39:10.400 --> 39:12.510
Mayor Tang used to live in Yunan.

39:12.760 --> 39:14.150
He said coming back this time

39:14.150 --> 39:15.680
was a return to simplicity.

39:15.880 --> 39:16.760
It brought back

39:16.760 --> 39:18.890
so much of how the New Year used to feel.

39:19.000 --> 39:20.550
I didn't expect him to be so proactive.

39:20.550 --> 39:22.150
Still so brave in middle age.

39:27.440 --> 39:28.300
What about you?

39:28.920 --> 39:30.760
So young, yet so old-fashioned.

39:31.410 --> 39:33.080
Are fireworks all you've got?

39:33.670 --> 39:35.360
The last time you set off fireworks

39:35.360 --> 39:37.230
was to celebrate getting into college.

39:37.230 --> 39:38.320
Why is it this time?

39:40.630 --> 39:41.550
This time...

39:45.000 --> 39:45.930
it's an apology.

39:52.510 --> 39:53.770
I accept your apology.

39:54.190 --> 39:55.400
I also need to say to you,

39:55.400 --> 39:56.000
I'm sorry.

39:57.280 --> 39:58.880
Actually, before the New Year,

39:58.880 --> 40:00.190
I already saw them.

40:00.960 --> 40:02.000
But I ran away.

40:03.110 --> 40:04.320
I wasn't afraid

40:04.320 --> 40:05.280
that you would say something

40:05.280 --> 40:06.550
I couldn't accept.

40:07.630 --> 40:09.400
It's just that when I thought about

40:09.400 --> 40:11.790
how a confrontation
might lead to an argument,

40:11.790 --> 40:12.800
I got scared.

40:15.550 --> 40:17.510
Xiaolan, you might have misunderstood.

40:17.510 --> 40:19.320
What you saw that day was likely

40:20.070 --> 40:21.440
Shi Kai's wife and son.

40:25.960 --> 40:26.710
Actually,

40:27.590 --> 40:29.390
the day you had the car accident,

40:31.320 --> 40:32.180
Shi Kai and I...

40:35.400 --> 40:35.920
Cheng.

40:36.030 --> 40:37.030
Is this the place?

40:37.550 --> 40:38.480
Should be here.

40:45.000 --> 40:45.760
Why would the person involved choose

40:45.760 --> 40:46.760
a place like this?

40:55.070 --> 40:55.510
Cheng,

40:56.360 --> 40:57.440
let's ask someone.

40:59.630 --> 41:00.000
Okay.

41:02.110 --> 41:02.810
Hello, Sir.

41:03.720 --> 41:04.580
May I ask...

41:49.790 --> 41:50.440
How is it?

41:50.840 --> 41:51.840
How is it, Doctor?

41:51.960 --> 41:53.490
We did everything we could.

42:05.550 --> 42:06.210
Zhou Cheng.

42:07.740 --> 42:08.440
Your friend just

42:08.440 --> 42:09.570
called the law firm,

42:09.960 --> 42:10.800
saying your partner was sent

42:10.800 --> 42:12.730
to Shengcheng People's Hospital.

42:17.400 --> 42:18.230
I wanted

42:19.030 --> 42:20.160
to tell you that day,

42:21.630 --> 42:23.230
but when I got to the hospital

42:23.590 --> 42:25.720
and saw something happened to you too,

42:26.880 --> 42:27.760
I really didn't know

42:27.760 --> 42:28.480
how to say it.
